## Strategy Pattern (Download Example)

### Strategy Interface
```python
# src/lib/download/base.py
class DownloadStrategy(ABC):
    @property
    @abstractmethod
    def name(self) -> str: ...
    
    @abstractmethod
    def download(self, url: str, target: Path, dry_run: bool = False) -> bool: ...
    
    def pre_download(self, target: Path) -> None: ...
    def post_download(self, target: Path) -> None: ...
    def on_interrupt(self, target: Path) -> None: ...
```

### Adding New Strategy
1. Create `src/lib/download/{name}.py`
2. Implement `{Name}Strategy(DownloadStrategy)`
3. Register in `DownloadManager._register_strategies()`
4. Add selection logic in `DownloadManager.get_strategy()`

